BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Finn: A New Musical â at the PB&J Cafe
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260501T210000
UID:bat-202605011900-finn-a-new-musical-at-the-pb-j-cafe@bloomingtonarts.t
 oday
DESCRIPTION:$. From the creator of Doc McStuffins and Vampirina\, Finn is 
 a heartwarming musical adventure about a young shark on the brink of growi
 ng up. As he prepares to join the fearsome Shark Guard\, Finn canât s
 hake the feeling that heâs different from the other sharks. Deep insi
 de\, he discovers a colorful fish inside himâa part of himself that l
 ongs to sparkle\, sing\, and dance. As Finn embarks on a journey of self-d
 iscovery\, friendship\, and adventure\, he finds the courage to be himself
 ! Fun for all ages!
LOCATION:Waldron Auditorium @ Waldron Arts Center
URL:https://seeconstellation.org/kids/finn/
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
