UID:bat-202605031900-sluice@bloomingtonarts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Sluice returns with *Companion*\, a record about losing fai
 th in the dream of musicâand finding it again. Led by Justin Morris\,
  the Durham four-piece channels indie rock\, country-tinged choruses\, and
  spiritual reflection into songs about love\, labor\, and second chances. 
 Itâs a story of disillusionment turned into determination\, where mus
 ic becomes not escape or stardom\, but companionship.
